definitionGroups.group: Any of several plants with a velvety leaf as a most notable feature.

entries.meaning: A tall Asian herb, Abutilon theophrasti, that has velvety heart-shaped leaves and yellow flowers.
Malva eriocalyx, tree mallow, native to Europe.
Limnocharis flava, yellow velvetleaf, an aquatic flowering plant native to southeast Asia.
Kalanchoe beharensis, a Madagascan succulent often kept as a houseplant.
